'''Nuknog''' was the language spoken by the [[Nuknog/Legends|Nuknog]] [[Species/Legends|species]], consisting of squeaks, barks, and gruff vocalizations. It utilized a simple alphabet.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

Most Nuknogs were fluent in both Nuknog and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

